### Controller Routes

- Frontend public: `auth='public'`, `website=True`
- API webhook: `auth='none'`, `csrf=False`, `type='json'`
- Portal user: `auth='user'`
- Format route: `/unitrade/{module}/{action}`

### Security

- Semua model custom wajib punya entry di `security/ir.model.access.csv`
- Gunakan `res.groups` untuk role-based access: group_unitrade_buyer, group_unitrade_seller
- Jangan simpan API key hardcoded — gunakan `ir.config_parameter`

## DATABASE MODELS UTAMA

- `res.users` — user akun, extend dengan: otp_code, otp_expiry, otp_attempt, reset_token
- `res.partner` — profil, extend dengan: username, gender, birth_date
- `unitrade.seller` — data penjual: user_id, nim, ktm_image, status, ocr_result
- `product.template` — extend dengan: condition (baru/bekas), seller_id, location_province, location_city
- `sale.order` — extend dengan: unitrade_status, delivery_id, payment_method
- `unitrade.review` — id, order_id, buyer_id, product_id, score(1-5), comment, is_moderated
- `unitrade.wishlist` — id, user_id, product_id (UNIQUE constraint)
- `unitrade.delivery` — id, order_id, gosend_order_id, tracking_status, origin_lat/lng, dest_lat/lng
- `unitrade.notification` — id, user_id, notif_type, title, body, is_read

## ORDER STATUS FLOW

draft → confirmed → shipped → done → cancelled
(Belum Bayar → Sedang Dikemas → Dikirim → Selesai → Dibatalkan)

## SELLER VERIFICATION FLOW

draft → pending → verified / rejected
(Input data → Menunggu admin → Disetujui / Ditolak)

## API INTEGRATIONS

### Midtrans

- Endpoint: https://app.sandbox.midtrans.com/snap/v1/transactions (sandbox)
- Auth: Basic base64(SERVER_KEY + ":")
- Webhook: POST /unitrade/payment/webhook
- Validasi signature: SHA512(order_id + status_code + gross_amount + SERVER_KEY)

### GoSend

- Create order: POST https://api.gojek.com/gojek/v3/send
- Webhook status: POST /unitrade/delivery/webhook
- Gunakan koordinat dari Google Places API untuk origin & destination

### PaddleOCR

- Input: gambar KTM base64 → decode → save temp → OCR → extract NIM & nama
- Confidence threshold: 0.7
- NIM regex UNISA: r'\b\d{10,12}\b' (sesuaikan dengan format aktual UNISA)

## COMMAND HARIAN

- Restart Odoo service: net stop odoo-server-17.0 && net start odoo-server-17.0
- Upgrade module: python odoo-bin -c odoo.conf -d unitrade_db -u [module_name] --stop-after-init
- Build Tailwind: cd custom-addons/unitrade_theme/tailwind && npm run build
- Watch Tailwind: npm run watch
- Clear asset cache: buka http://localhost:8069/web?debug=assets

## DONT'S — JANGAN LAKUKAN INI

- Jangan edit file di dalam C:\Program Files\Odoo 17.0.20260217\server\odoo\ (akan hilang saat update)
- Jangan pakai @tailwind base (konflik Bootstrap)
- Jangan hardcode API key di Python file
- Jangan pakai jQuery ($) langsung di template — gunakan OWL component
- Jangan skip entry ir.model.access.csv — akan error saat install module
- Jangan lupa `__init__.py` di setiap folder models/ dan controllers/
